thread.title: Gregory Moses
thread.title_full: NZ Rockshop reviewed by Gregory Moses

author: Gregory Moses
title: Gregory Moses
text:
Went to Henderson store on Saturday 18/03/2017, the staff and management team there were fantastic, I hadn't been there in 30 odd years, many things had changed but the service and smiles were still there.
Chri's was to say , exceptional, he couldn't do enough for me, he went well over the next level to make sure my visit and sale went smoothly and effectively.
Thanks heaps Chris
